quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  26,70,Geukheun bak ayahgeuh ngon bak kaom d Geuh gata bandum peue nyan taseumah
  26,71,Jikheun dum kamoe meuseumah patong Beurhala bandum han kamoe keubah
  26,72,Geukheun boh na deuh jideungo gata Watee tabaca peue tameung peugah
  26,73,Ek jibri le jih peue nyang munapheu“ʻat í Got pih meularat teuh ek jipeuglah
  26,74,Jikheun dum kamoe meu-eu yah kamoe Bandum atra nyoe dilee geuseumah A
  26,75,Geukheun taeukeuh nyang taseumah nyan
  26,76,Le gata dum nyan ngon ayah-ayah Ngon yah-yah gata dum nyang ka dilee
  26,77,Bandum nyan sitree lon musoh leupah 1 Meulengkan Tuhan nyang Po alam nyoe
  26,78,Nyang peujeuet lon nyoe phon manyak leupah Neubri peutunyok keu lon ‘oh lheueh nyan
  26,79,Neubri makanan ngon ie puleh grah
  26,80,Watee saket lon Neupeupuleh le
  26,81,Lon Neupeumate pih han soe teugah Neupeuudep lon lom ‘oh Iheueh mate
  26,82,Neuampon sabe watee lon salah Meunapsu lon that Neuampon dacha Jan haro hara watee Neubalah Uroe kiamat haro hara that
  26,83,Neubri hikmat keu lon ya Allah € Neupeusapat lon ngon ureueng shaleh
  26,84,Neupeujroh leubeh nan lon gop peugah Bak ureueng dudoe nan lon beu beuna
  26,85,Neubri pusaka churuga indah Churuga nikmat lon tueng pusaka Neubri keu hamba wahe ya Allah
  26,86,Lom Neupeuampon dacha ayah lon Sabab ayah lon sisat ka salah
  26,87,Lom pih ulon nyoe bek Neubri ‘ayeb Uroe geubangket malee lon leupah
  26,88,Atra ngon aneuk hana guna le ‘Oh uroe page ka teuka sudah
  26,89,Meulengkan soe-soe nyang jak bak Tuhan Ate jih iman nyang gleh sileupah
  26,90,Teuma geupeutoe keunan churuga Bak ureueng takwa iman keu Allah
  26,91,Diureueng sisat leumah nuraka
  26,92,Geutanyong sigra ho ka tuhankah Peue nyang ka seumah nyang bukan Tuhan
  26,93,Ho ka dum jih nyan kacuba peugah ž Na jitulong kah atawa droejih
  26,94,Geulungkop dum jih lam apui mirah Awak nyang sisat meusapat ngon jih
  26,95,Lom tentra Iblih sinan geukeubah Sipai Iblih bandum di sinan
  26,96,Meudawa yoh nyan meuplah-plah babah
  26,97,Deumi nyo Tuhan kamoe nyoe sisat
  26,98,Gata dum meuhat kamoe jak seumah Sabab meupeusa gata ngon Tuhan Nyang Po dum alam nyang Maha Murah
  26,99,Kon ureueng laen peusisat kamoe Nyoekeuh awak nyoe nyang peubuet salah
  26,100,Hana chupeuʻat le soe keu kamoe
  26,101,Rakan dum nyang toe pih tan le leumah
  26,102,Adak meu geutem geupeuwoe kamoe Meuiman kamoe jinoe le bagah
  26,103,Bandum atra nyan cit jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Keu jih bandum nyan hana phaedah
  26,104,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah